 Photo taken on Dec. 15, 2021 shows the 2021 Shenzhen Global Investment Promotion Conference in Shenzhen, south China's Guangdong Province. More than 260 deals were signed at the conference, clinching contractual investments of more than 820 billion yuan (about 128.8 billion U.S. dollars). (Xinhua/Liang Xu)  Photo taken on Dec. 15, 2021 shows the 2021 Shenzhen Global Investment Promotion Conference in Shenzhen, south China's Guangdong Province. More than 260 deals were signed at the conference, clinching contractual investments of more than 820 billion yuan (about 128.8 billion U.S. dollars). (Xinhua/Liang Xu)